{"tid":1447073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無可能利用黑警假扮示威者呢招借力打力？","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:33:48.000Z","uid":62811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b24a9ff31ffc9d34b7516774c2c27e883e88b0","tid":1447073,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"黑警呢招雙面刃<br />\n除左可以確認已經發生咗嘅事係狗嘅所為之外<br />\n<br />\n仲可以計劃扮演扮緊示威者嘅黑警(用一啲共同特徵例如帶單邊耳機，綠色螢光棒，身材高大)<br />\n<br />\n跟住就做出公安先會做嘅行為 例如講蝗語(好似新城市嗰條片已經搞到人心惶惶，前提要度好個劇本，同保障上鏡手足嘅安全)<br />\n<br />\n總之個整體概念就係人人都可以扮扮緊示威者嘅黑警，善用呢個身分繼續係民意戰上抹黑黑警。"},{"pid":"54fea830bba8d38b42779243f4772046a48b0a0a","tid":1447073,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:38:06.000Z","msg":"721 警黑合作"},{"pid":"8dc03d241ffc39c634906dad95786b1ded0656bf","tid":1447073,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日邊個番工 邊個就係港豬<br />\n全民塞鐵封路, 有狗打狗</span></span>"},{"pid":"f3c30dce429b7eb105814f51afeef1c8d4ab3116","tid":1447073,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c490b02f697f4be77446df127d6e4cb6d4c2637b","tid":1447073,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3PmxAk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3PmxAk.jpg&h=1cfccbc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qz1gmtG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqz1gmtG.png&h=8385db6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvOuGtJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmvOuGtJ.png&h=ade366f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c938f977539bb1ae9427723e7bc502c6299c021","tid":1447073,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"唔洗抹黑<br />\n已經有合理懷疑"},{"pid":"6c685992fa158825d050420e61f8e14607b443cc","tid":1447073,"uid":4948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:05.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=3e0ffec3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTGXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=e534138e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"9fcd987fc0255e18f43629b6972c6e35870b123f","tid":1447073,"uid":287740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:23:41.000Z","msg":"有黑警混入示威者都唔割蓆！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447238</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n重要post 請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea9a089d588b17d3902c8a7abc59e4330ee1438","tid":1447073,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c938f977539bb1ae9427723e7bc502c6299c021","tid":1447073,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"唔洗抹黑<br />\n已經有合理懷疑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"我指係做啲佢地未做 唔願意比人知嘅野<br />\n針住佢死穴打落去，全世界都知係香港武警做嘅"}]}